    {
      "type": "text",
      "id": "ai_prompt_detail_text",
      "x": 464.87890625,
      "y": 582.814453125,
      "width": 283.59375,
      "height": 137.5,
      "text": "Prompt → Claude:\n  JSON-serialized mart data\n  (stats, h2h results, standings)\n\nClaude → Response:\n  Structured HTML with CSS classes\n  (f1-narrative-hook, f1-narrative-bullets)\n\nCaching: SHA-256(prompt) → skip if unchanged\nEvidence: {@html} renders card per pairing",
      "originalText": "Prompt → Claude:\n  JSON-serialized mart data\n  (stats, h2h results, standings)\n\nClaude → Response:\n  Structured HTML with CSS classes\n  (f1-narrative-hook, f1-narrative-bullets)\n\nCaching: SHA-256(prompt) → skip if unchanged\nEvidence: {@html} renders card per pairing",
      "fontSize": 11,
      "fontFamily": 3,
      "textAlign": "left",
      "verticalAlign": "middle",
      "strokeColor": "#22c55e",
