      "y": 615.1880693791234,
      "width": 199.8046875,
      "height": 165,
      "text": "GitHub Pages ✅ LIVE\n\nURL: singhpriyanshu5.github.io\n     /f1-rivalry-dashboard/\n\nStatic site: all Snowflake data\nbaked in at build time\n\nCI: npm ci → postinstall →\n  patch-package applies patches\n  → npm run sources → build\n  → deploy to Pages",
      "originalText": "GitHub Pages ✅ LIVE\n\nURL: singhpriyanshu5.github.io\n     /f1-rivalry-dashboard/\n\nStatic site: all Snowflake data\nbaked in at build time\n\nCI: npm ci → postinstall →\n  patch-package applies patches\n  → npm run sources → build\n  → deploy to Pages",
